{"word":"G2141 - εὐπορέω - euporéō - yoo-por-eh'-o - Ability","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐπορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euporéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-por-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ability</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திராணி"},{"paragraph":"to be well off, have means"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2090 - ἑτοιμάζω - hetoimázō - het-oy-mad'-zo/2090\">G2090</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G4197 - πορεία - poreía - por-i'-ah/4197\">G4197</a>; (intransitively) to <i>be good</i> for <i>passing</i> through, that is, (figuratively) <i>have</i> pecuniary <i>means:</i> - ability.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}